{"tid":85282,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"10 polo1.4 vs 04 jazz1.3","createTime":"2017-01-18T08:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T09:10:00.000Z","uid":38930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"46d6966929cbedb93e00dfcf9b03af12444c809d","tid":85282,"uid":38930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T08:17:41.000Z","msg":"向位巴打好,岩岩早幾日拎左P仔<br />\n<br />\n目前係網上面見到呢兩部車,如果P仔操車邊部好d?<br />\n<br />\npolo係靚仔d,車主講14年換左一次極力子<br />\n無天窗 72000咪<br />\n<br />\njazz就有天窗同後泊鏡 11萬咪車身同樣係幾靚仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係jazz既價錢加多2萬左右就有polo,係怕polo如果一但死波箱個價錢真係抬都唔洗抬,唔知polo個deg易唔易壞?同事架10年golf tsi係保養期去抬左一次報價要5萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果jazz有乜野衰應該就乜車房都有得整同埋零件會好便?<br />\n<br />\n謝謝各位"},{"pid":"7aaa2f148854eac6bfb80436a730570af38e37bd","tid":85282,"uid":38930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T08:22:26.000Z","msg":"另外一個月預8k養唔知得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n<br />\n油2000 (新西返九龍每日60公里來回)<br />\n兩邊車場 4000<br />\n假日/消耗品/雜項 2000"},{"pid":"0d2702cc4247e12c40309ee3aa21ea74bd6c313d","tid":85282,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:42:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外一個月預8k養唔知得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n<br />\n油2000 (新西返九龍每日60公里來回)<br />\n兩邊車場 4000<br />\n假日/消耗品/雜項 2000</blockquote><br />\n差唔多，車場真係好撚貴。理論上 jazz應該慳油d。"},{"pid":"1ef3a8bf63d7c2892f4ccb2c5665c2cb77c70e3d","tid":85282,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:13:18.000Z","msg":"Jazz 第二代啦"},{"pid":"d1465f815a0a830593104c73dd381a07277ccf7f","tid":85282,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:18:40.000Z","msg":"上個月出左 10年 Polo 1.4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n油錢 $0.9 左右<br />\n暫時未有咩問題, 波箱驚有事既話就停車空波, 塞車就轉+-波, 咁樣會耐用D (好似係)"},{"pid":"87990216a94f598f36ca012fdd9d79d9817b3979","tid":85282,"uid":38930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:34:31.000Z","msg":"岩岩我上網睇過，發現jazz cvt 跪都一樣大獲，但好彩遇到有零件6-8千搞到？<br />\n可能粗用用jazz仔會好d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5daad0cbba34f61ba20c856f13fc9af27985d52a","tid":85282,"uid":38930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:36:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上個月出左 10年 Polo 1.4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n油錢 $0.9 左右<br />\n暫時未有咩問題, 波箱驚有事既話就停車空波, 塞車就轉+-波, 咁樣會耐用D (好似係)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網又睇過話停車（紅綠燈時間）唔好啪N因為齒輪換得多仲大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而塞車轉+-唔比佢上去轉波就係正確"},{"pid":"a57046453485c6e4c04b3b01863fff151778e0ff","tid":85282,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T02:49:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上個月出左 10年 Polo 1.4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n油錢 $0.9 左右<br />\n暫時未有咩問題, 波箱驚有事既話就停車空波, 塞車就轉+-波, 咁樣會耐用D (好似係)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網又睇過話停車（紅綠燈時間）唔好啪N因為齒輪換得多仲大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而塞車轉+-唔比佢上去轉波就係正確</blockquote><br />\n唔係掛 我FD就算渣FIT 好似都係CVT佢都係停燈位轉空波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ffc5ca30a7f0484f9eb82e380a746e21e029fc6","tid":85282,"uid":20602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T03:00:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上個月出左 10年 Polo 1.4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n油錢 $0.9 左右<br />\n暫時未有咩問題, 波箱驚有事既話就停車空波, 塞車就轉+-波, 咁樣會耐用D (好似係)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網又睇過話停車（紅綠燈時間）唔好啪N因為齒輪換得多仲大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而塞車轉+-唔比佢上去轉波就係正確</blockquote><br />\n唔係掛 我FD就算渣FIT 好似都係CVT佢都係停燈位轉空波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果AT, 停車係唔需要轉空波, 除非你大塞車長停, 又或者想鬆腳。<br />\n<br />\n因為你轉D波-空波-D波-空波, 你齒輪經常咬合仲傷個波箱<br />\n<br />\n利申:FIT"},{"pid":"606f5e32224ffa2bbcf6f5d00bd0afdcd0d62dbd","tid":85282,"uid":20602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T03:06:47.000Z","msg":"回返樓主, VW 波箱易出事係通病, 有人有事有人冇事, 主要睇你好唔好彩, 就算上架都睇唔到。<br />\n<br />\nJAZZ就命賤易養, 一來通街都係零件,二來隨便入一間車房都識整。<br />\n<br />\n如果P牌, 我覺得用高年份同易維修車會較好。因為你出入車場, HI花撞親, 唔去整都冇咁肉赤。況且JAZZ個價比較硬, 你兩年後再拎出去可能都執得返1,2萬。<br />\n<br />\n你P牌又成日出車, 真心買架JAZZ玩下先練下手會比較好。<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 如果你堅持想買歐洲車或者VW, 不如買GOLF好過POLO, 駕駛體驗好好多"},{"pid":"c7145db00489b703a64a93c2d7d2cfd1d0ec2cae","tid":85282,"uid":38930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T04:04:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>回返樓主, VW 波箱易出事係通病, 有人有事有人冇事, 主要睇你好唔好彩, 就算上架都睇唔到。<br />\n<br />\nJAZZ就命賤易養, 一來通街都係零件,二來隨便入一間車房都識整。<br />\n<br />\n如果P牌, 我覺得用高年份同易維修車會較好。因為你出入車場, HI花撞親, 唔去整都冇咁肉赤。況且JAZZ個價比較硬, 你兩年後再拎出去可能都執得返1,2萬。<br />\n<br />\n你P牌又成日出車, 真心買架JAZZ玩下先練下手會比較好。<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 如果你堅持想買歐洲車或者VW, 不如買GOLF好過POLO, 駕駛體驗好好多</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打，我都主諗jazz，因為真係操車我無乜所謂<br />\n係怕車壞無件整又貴就真麻煩，不過朋友叫我睇埋先無壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我約左兩架"},{"pid":"5a465c9fe0a627697edc4149ee89e207e270e3ff","tid":85282,"uid":57109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T04:10:16.000Z","msg":"你其實BUDGET 幾多?"},{"pid":"f94d8b5a307606f272daed5edfa3767bca7b6a5b","tid":85282,"uid":17759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T04:33:25.000Z","msg":"買jazz啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWn6fp9ydCDbbCb1bPwn9giLTbs5iH4cznZesyQ9Hto9i?filename=4x73u6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4x73u6c.jpg&h=c52572d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a02803603bd4281a6c7d54a1f46bd7ed835dc304","tid":85282,"uid":38930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T06:55:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你其實BUDGET 幾多?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n4萬左右 當然3萬以下最好 因為操車用唔需要靚"},{"pid":"985eb2e4bf84fd0a55530a93b7f770dc0563850f","tid":85282,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:02:31.000Z","msg":"唔睇車款, 應該係10年好好多啦<br />\n12年已變牛肺, 你就唔好信11萬啦, 行左13年車, 搵人篤里數有幾難<br />\n<br />\n04都就算本田都會壞波箱<br />\n<br />\n一係買架08既JAZZ, 可能係最好選擇"},{"pid":"d33533878e1fb65086127a4294db5efb1740ee26","tid":85282,"uid":13908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:19:52.000Z","msg":"Polo club 暫時只聽過有一人死波箱<br />\n<br />\n好多人宜家 10萬公里都冇事<br />\n<br />\n每3萬換一換波油<br />\n<br />\n其實 polo 冇咩野壞，又紮實又好揸過日本車<br />\n<br />\n但二手價 jazz 應該強啲<br />\n<br />\n建議買 polo 1.2 ，有 turbo 爽死"},{"pid":"21f105e798be537d4c4aba296679197e9eeb65ab","tid":85282,"uid":13908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:23:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你其實BUDGET 幾多?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n4萬左右 當然3萬以下最好 因為操車用唔需要靚</blockquote><br />\n咁嘅 budget 難搵啲靚盤 polo 喎"},{"pid":"56dca2e969bfca28baf285410b6d695c2efb70db","tid":85282,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:26:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你其實BUDGET 幾多?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n4萬左右 當然3萬以下最好 因為操車用唔需要靚</blockquote><br />\n咁嘅 budget 難搵啲靚盤 polo 喎</blockquote><br />\n如果比樓主執到4萬既10 Polo, 可能都有伏味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fd9579dc379e9129b485f843c49bd0c2962f96","tid":85282,"uid":13908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:28:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n4萬左右 當然3萬以下最好 因為操車用唔需要靚</blockquote><br />\n咁嘅 budget 難搵啲靚盤 polo 喎</blockquote><br />\n如果比樓主執到4萬既10 Polo, 可能都有伏味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一係高咪一係好殘一係炒過"},{"pid":"21282b9137176a5b0f7104e07ff7223b4b585332","tid":85282,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:2